summary: AN ORDINANCE approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 6466, and repealing Ordinance No. 100097, dated July 14, 1971, in connection therewith, for the improvement of HARBOR AVENUE SOUTHWEST from Southwest Florida Street to approximately 975 feet northwesterly thereof; and a certain other avenue; by constructing sanitary sewers and otherwise improving the same; under Ordinance No. 99427, and levying and assessing the amounts ... estblishing a Local Improvement Fund, and amending Section 4 of Ordinance No. 99427.
